      "testType": "TestType-Assay",
      "testConditions": {
        "en": "Transfer 20 mL of Formalin Water, measured exactly, to a 100-mL volumetric flask containing 2.5 mL of 1 mol/L sodium hydroxide VS, and add water to make 100 mL. Pipet 10 mL of this solution, and proceed as directed in the Assay under Formalin. Each mL of 0.05 mol/L iodine VS ＝ 1.501 mg of CH2O"
      }
    }
  ],
